 <arm>
   <uof name="Geometrically_Bounded_Surface">
     <description>
The Geometrically_Bounded_Surface UoF specifies the data structure for the representation of surface models that consist of
points, elementary or sculptured curves, and elementary or sculptured
surfaces. Geometry shall be bounded. No topological entities are used for bounding. 
